at 20:00 UTC in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org. 
[LOG](../../../logs/2010/2010-10-13-log.txt)


## President's Report

Bdale reports that he and Jonathan had started work on long discussed
replacement for the SPI website, based on ikiwiki, git + markdown. The
new structure is licensed CC-by-SA 3.0 and there's enough there to be
able to get an idea of where we're going.


