## Any other business

David mentioned that OFTC were in the midst of their annual elections.
Jonathan pointed out that
[PgWest](https://www.postgresqlconference.org/) was on at the start of
November. Bdale commented that he'd spoken to Bradley Kuhn of the
conservancy and congratulated him on his soon-to-be paid exec director
role there. The relationship between SPI and the conservancy is good and
both parties wish to keep it that way and point projects at whichever is
the better "hosting organisation".

